Description: DPOL_PYRFU - Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. In addition to polymerase activity, this DNA polymerase exhibits 3' to 5' exonuclease activity. From Pyrococcus furiosus (strain ATCC 43587 / DSM 3638 / JCM 8422 / Vc1).
β-lactamase; bla; confers resistance to ampicillin, carbenicillin, and related antibiotics
transcription terminator for bacteriophage T7 RNA polymerase
bidirectional E. coli tonB-P14 transcription terminator
LacZα fragment of β-galactosidase; lacZ fragment
